## âœ… 1. Apply a Test GPO to the Workstations OU

Letâ€™s apply a simple GPO that will visibly confirm it's working â€” for example, weâ€™ll display a legal banner on logon.

## ðŸ›  Steps to Create and Link the GPO:
1. On your Domain Controller, open Group Policy Management

2. Right-click the Workstations OU â†’ Create a GPO in this domain, and Link it hereâ€¦

3. Name it something like: Workstation - Legal Banner

