`Computer Configuration > Policies > Windows Settings > Security Settings > Local Policies > Security Options`

Set:

Interactive logon: Message title for users attempting to log on â†’ e.g., `Helpdesk Notice`

Interactive logon: Message text for users attempting to log on â†’ e.g., `Unauthorized access is prohibited. All activity may be monitored.`

5. Close the editor and run:
`gpupdate /force`

on your WIN10 client (or reboot it) to test.

## âœ… You should now see a banner before login â€” this confirms the Workstations OU GPO is applying correctly.

