ðŸ“œ 2. Add a Script to Log Which Computer a User Logs In From
Weâ€™ll use a Logon Script via GPO to write the username and computer name to a central text file on your Domain Controller (or shared folder).

ðŸ“ Prep Shared Log Folder:
1. On your Domain Controller, create a folder like:
`C:\LoginLogs`
